fields.name: Push-up
fields.description: A push-up (or press-up in British English) is a common calisthenics exercise beginning from the prone position.

fields.name: Crunch
fields.description: The crunch is one of the most popular abdominal exercises.

fields.name: Plank
fields.description: The plank is an isometric core strength exercise that involves maintaining a position similar to a push-up for the maximum possible time.
